@node Main "Wilinx - Documentation"

                           'Wilinx' 1.0

                        by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Wilinx' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to move a coloured
'wire' from the upper left, to its 'receiving position', which is
located at the lower right on the 7 by 7 spaces game board.

  To do so, you have to move the wire, piece by piece, either
horizontally, vertically or diagonally ...but you also have to move
'neutral tiles' that are in the way. Also keep in mind that none of
the wire links can be 'stretched' by more than one unit.

  Have fun!

